# Generated Architecture pages (see scripts/sync-arch-docs.mjs). These are
# copied from docs/ at the start of every build (local, CI, docs.yml) so
# they can never drift stale in git relative to their sources. Only
# docs/architecture/index.md (hand-written) is committed.
/docs/architecture/decisions.md
/docs/architecture/recorder-correctness.md
/docs/architecture/motion-recording.md

# Generated Camera Compatibility page (see scripts/gen-camera-compat.mjs).
# Rendered from data/camera-compatibility.json at the start of every build
# (local, CI, docs.yml, Docker) so it can never drift from the source data.
/docs/cameras/compatibility.md

